{"title_page": "Kamila Tuszy\u0144ska", "text_new": "{{Blacklisted-links|1=\n*https://comicsforum.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/nncore-helsinki-abstracts.pdf\n*:''Triggered by <code>\\bfiles\\.wordpress\\.com\\b</code> on the global blacklist''|bot=Cyberbot II|invisible=false}}\n{{Orphan|date=August 2016}}\n\n'''Kamila Tuszy\u0144ska''' \u2013 PhD in humanities (literary, linguistics, culture and media studies), a [[Narratology|narratologist]], researcher in [[media studies]] and [[comics]] theoretician.\n\nA lecturer,<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ips.polon.uw.edu.pl/teamduty.php?gid=7|title=Zak\u0142ad Retoryki i Medi\u00f3w  [Department of Rhetoric and Media]|last=|first=|date=|website=Instytut Polonistyki Stosowanej, Uniwersytet Warszawski [Institute of Applied Polish Studies, University of Warsaw]|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-24}}</ref> speaker, columnist and peer reviewer for [[:pl:Zeszyty Komiksowe|\"Zeszyty Komiksowe\"]]  [''Comic Books''], journal co-financed by the [[Ministry of Culture and National Heritage of the Republic of Poland]]; a member of the editorial staff of [[\"Napis\"]] magazine published by the Institute of Literary Research of the [[Polish Academy of Science]] (IBL PAN).\n\nAn author of articles and papers about [[comics]] and an author of the very first book <ref>{{Cite book|title=Narracja w powie\u015bci graficznej|last=Tuszy\u0144ska|first=Kamila|publisher=Wydawnictwo Naukowe PWN|year=|isbn=9788301185527|location=Warsaw|pages=23|via=}}</ref> (''Narracja w powie\u015bci graficznej'', Warsaw, [[Polish Scientific Publishers PWN|Wydawnictwo Naukowe PWN [Polish Scientific Publishers PWN],]] 2015, {{ISBN|9788301185527}}; [''[[Narratology of Graphic Novels: an Introduction]]'']), exclusively devoted to [[Narrative|narrative strategies]] in American and European [[graphic novel]]s, in which she comments on the 371 original source texts from the research areas from the [[United States|USA]], [[Western Europe]], [[Central and Eastern Europe]] and proposes brand new research tools, terms and concepts.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ksiegarnia.pwn.pl/Narracja-w-powiesci-graficznej,391906503,p.html|title=Narracja w powie\u015bci graficznej [Narratology to Graphic Novels: an Introduction]|last=|first=|date=|website=Polish Scientific Publishers PWN|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-24}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nShe defended a doctoral dissertation entitled ''Narrative strategies in comics. Between elite and popular culture'' at the Department of Rhetoric and Media''',''' [[University of Warsaw]].\n\nA member of the Third Regions of Literature Studies Group affiliated with the [[Polish Academy of Sciences|Polish Academy of Sciences (PAN)]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ibl.waw.pl/en/abouttheinstitute/institutions-affiliated-to-ibl-pan/third-regions-of-literature-studies-group|title=Third Regions of Literature Studies Group|last=|first=|date=|website=Institute of Literary Research of the Polish Academy of Sciences|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-24}}</ref> and of the Laboratory of Occasional and Applied Literature, [[University of Warsaw]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ilp.uw.edu.pl/laboratory-of-occasional-and-consumer-literature/|title=Laboratory of Occasional and Consumer Literature|last=|first=|date=|website=Institute of Polish Literature, Faculty of Polish Studies at the University of Warsaw|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-24}}</ref> where her subject matter is comics.\n\nAs a [[Narratology|narratologist]] she is a member of the [[European Narratology Network (ENN)]]<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=http://en.kamilatuszynska.com/about-me.html|title=About Me|last=|first=|date=|website=Kamila Tuszy\u0144ska, Phd|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-24}}</ref> and of the [[International Society for the Study of Narrative (ISSN)|International Society for the Study of Narrative (ISSN''')''']]<ref name=\":0\" />'''.'''\n\nAs a [[comics]] theoretician she is the only one Polish member of the [[International Bande Dessin\u00e9e Society (IBDS)]]''',''' the [[Nordic Network for Comics Research (NNCORE)|Nordic Network for Comics Research (NNCORE''')''']] and of the [[Comics Studies Society (CSS)]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.panteon.pl/Artykul/269|title=Panteon - stolica superbohater\u00f3w - [WYWIAD] Wywiad z dr Kamil\u0105 Tuszy\u0144sk\u0105|last=Kicman|first=Pawe\u0142|date=|website=panteon.pl|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-24}}</ref>\n\nA speaker at [[Comics Arts Conference|international comics conferences]], including the [[San Diego Comic-Con|Comic Con (California)]].<ref>Among others: Comics Art Conference, Comic-Con 2013 (USA), http://www.comic-con.org/wca/2013/comics-arts-conference [retrieved 2016-08-24], NNCORE 2013 International Conference in Comics Studies (University of Helsinki, Finland),https://comicsforum.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/nncore-helsinki-abstracts.pdf [retrieved 2016-08-24], PROJECT: Comic Con, POP Girls! 2015 (USA)http://www.projectcomiccon.com/?page_id=2714 [retrieved 2016-08-24]</ref>\n\nFor years in various institutions she has been conducting thesis seminars and original courses, such as: the poetics of comics, verbal-and-visual workshops, artistic and applied narratives, writing on the Internet: theory and practice, workshops for columnists, journalism and press workshops as well as local and environmental media.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://en.kamilatuszynska.com/courses.html|title=Conducted courses|last=|first=|date=|website=Kamila Tuszy\u0144ska, PhD|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-24}}</ref>\n\nFeatured as an expert in the media, including Polish television: [[TVP Info]], [[TVP Kultura]], radio: [[TOK FM|Tok FM]], [[Polskie Radio Program IV|Czw\u00f3rka Polskie Radio]], [[Polskie Radio Program III|Tr\u00f3jka - Program Trzeci Polskiego Radia]], [[Program 1 Polskiego Radia]], [[Polskie Radio Program II|Program 2 Polskiego Radia]], [[Radio RDC,]] [[Kampus]] and press: [[Newsweek Polska|Newsweek]], [[Gazeta Prawna]], [[bankier.pl]], [[NaTemat.pl]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://en.kamilatuszynska.com/media.html|title=Selected radio appearances and quotes in articles (in Polish)|last=|first=|date=|website=Kamila Tuszy\u0144ska, Phd|publisher=|access-date=2016-08-24}}</ref>\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://en.kamilatuszynska.com/ Kamila Tuszy\u0144ska homepage]\n* [https://scholar.google.pl/citations?hl=pl&imq=Kamila+Tuszynsk&user=z3dR1goAAAAJ Kamila Tuszy\u0144ska, Phd - Google Scholar Citations]\n* [http://nauka-polska.pl/dhtml/raporty/ludzieNauki?rtype=opis&objectId=246367&lang=pl Kamila Tuszy\u0144ska, Phd - Polish Science Database] ([[O\u015brodek Przetwarzania Informacji|OPI]])\n* Konrad Wysocki, [http://gpcodziennie.pl/49702-polskikomiksdorownujeswiatowejczolowce.html#.V743KZiLTIV Polski komiks dor\u00f3wnuje \u015bwiatowej czo\u0142\u00f3wce. Wywiad z dr Kamil\u0105 Tuszy\u0144sk] \u0105, Gazeta Codzienna, 22.04.2016, s. 12\n* Micha\u0142  Chudoli\u0144ski, [http://www.2plus3d.pl/kwartalnik/56 Niem\u0119skie rysowanie.Rozmowa z Kamil\u0105 Tuszy\u0144sk\u0105 o kobiecej stronie komiksu], 2 + 3 D, 56 (III/2015), s.  90-98\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tuszy\u0144ska, Kamila}}\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Polish academics]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Polish women academics]]\n", "text_old": "{{Blacklisted-links|1=\n*https://comicsforum.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/nncore-helsinki-abstracts.pdf\n*:''Triggered by <code>\\bfiles\\.wordpress\\.com\\b</code> on the global blacklist''|bot=Cyberbot II|invisible=false}}\n{{Orphan|date=August 2016}}\n\n'''Kamila Tuszy\u0144ska''' \u2013 PhD in humanities (literary, linguistics, culture and media studies), a [[Narratology|narratologist]], researcher in [[media studies]] and [[comics]] theoretician.\n\nA lecturer,<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ips.polon.uw.edu.pl/teamduty.php?gid=7|title=Zak\u0142ad Retoryki i Medi\u00f3w  [Department of Rhetoric and Media]|last=|first=|date=|website=Instytut Polonistyki Stoso